data.meta_description: Classic Autoworx is an internet based classic car, hot rod, muscle car and custom vehicle provider that offers the finest quality vehicles from daily drivers, to high end show and collector quality vehicles.
data.text:
---------------------------------------------------------------------

01/27/2011- We are pleased to announce the unveiling of the Dodge D100 pickup project on January 29th 2011 at Smarty's Garage - Car Show and Open House event. The project is a cooperative effort between Classic Autoworx and Razor's Hot Rods and Customs to show what can be done with an unconventional build platform. In conjunction with Smarty's Garage and Razor's Hot Rods and Customs, we'll be on hand to show the truck as well as answer any questions event attendees may have. Come on out and enjoy a great day in Phoenix filled with classics, muscle cars and hot rods, live music and refreshments.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

4/21/11 - Classic Autoworx is very pleased to announce that

we have teamed up with Hoot's Rod and Custom to bring to market their beautiful and exciting brand of Hot Rods, Muscle Cars and Classics. If you aren't familiar with Hoot's Rod and Custom, you might be familiar with at least one of their builds. Below you'll find the most well known example of their craftsmanship, Bob "Hoot" Gibson's 1956 Ford. Truckin' Magazine did a spread on this vehicle. Here's a link:

http://www.truckinweb.com/features/0913tr_1956_ford_f100/index.html

For more information on Hoot's Rod and Custom, feel free to give them a call or stop in.

Hoot's Rod and Custom

(623) 535-3776

5/12/11- Classic Autoworx is pleased to announce that we've developed a business relationship with Direct Express, Inc. A well established shipping and freight carrier that has been in business since 1986! They provide Auto shipping to points all over the globe.

For more information, please have a look at their website:

http://www.shipdei.com/
